name: Leviatein
text: Probably the best service from dominos I’ve ever received! They were fast and friendly, and when I got my food, it was nice and hot, and looked fantastic as well! I personally give this store a 8/10

name: christopher brusich
text: Our order is always accurate, and they deliver quickly.

name: Allan Conner
text: Got a large pizza and it had areas with no cheese on it. Like multiple 2 inch wide sections. The areas that did have cheese were very thin. We paid full price for the pizza too. Extremely disappointed.

name: Chuck Towery
text:
Terrible customer service. Tried to order online 3-topping large $7.99 but wouldn’t go through. Very disinterested employee said “Oh we don’t do that here.”
What??!!

name: AlaskanFox
text: Extremely double check your order because I asked for a small pizza, and they gave me this full on greased up pizza. It was terrible and I got my money back from that. The whole pizza just full of grease.

name: Robert Carrasco
text: Every time I decide to go here, there’s some issue. Usually the employees seem annoyed, and it takes a very long time. And other times they just say they don’t have whatever I just asked for. Very strange how they just don’t care.

name: brandon garza
text: Be sure to double check your order. This Domino's always tends to forget the dipping sauces that you order
